<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٥ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلهم:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" الدُّنْيَا سَاعَة فَجَعلهَا طَاعَةً "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٠٦ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" الدُّنْيَا مَزْرَعَةُ الآخِرَةِ "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٠٧ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" <span style="color:#707070">[الدِّينُ]</span> : التَّعْظِيمُ لأَمْرِ اللَّهِ، وَالشَّفَقَةُ عَلَى خَلْقِ اللَّهِ "</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>